        <question>
            <text>Volume of O2 (STP) required for complete combustion of 1 mole Propane (C3H8)? ____ L.</text>
            <option id="A">112</option><option id="B">22.4</option><option id="C">44.8</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>C3H8 + 5O2 -&gt; 3CO2 + 4H2O. 5 x 22.4 = 112.</explanation></question>
        <question>
            <text>Equivalent weight of KMnO4 in basic medium (MnO4- -&gt; MnO2) is ____.</text>
